{"tid":945247,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 年任天堂 Switch 全球銷售量將超越 PS4","createTime":"2018-12-17T17:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T09:12:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a512b4b14670589e8e45b3ccd2886315d25dfde","tid":945247,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"Nintendo Switch 今年交出非常亮眼的成績單，隨著 Sony 2019 年將首度缺席美國 E3 遊戲展，調研單位 Strategy Analytics 認為，明年很可能是任天堂重返硬體市場控制權的一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/31064014/1031-nintendo-switch-sell-624x328.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F31064014%2F1031-nintendo-switch-sell-624x328.png&h=abfdb76c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n過去數年，Sony 主機一直都在市佔保持領先地位，2018 年也是如此，從 Strategy Analytics 數據來看，2018 年 PS 系列市占幾乎達所有遊戲主機的一半，其中 84% 是 PS4 或 PS4 Pro。<br />\n<br />\n然而 2019 年情勢可能會開始出現轉變。Strategy Analytics 估計，2019 年任天堂將在全球售出 1,730 萬台 Nintendo Switch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，超過 Sony 1710 萬台 PS4 系列以及微軟的 1,000 萬台 Xbox One 系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n這個數字將使任天堂時隔 10 年再次重返銷售寶座。由於任天堂史上最大規模新作《任天堂明星大亂鬥特別版》（Super Smash Bros）將於近期推出，再加上 2019 年 Nintendo Switch 將改版的傳言，Strategy Analytics 的預測也是其來有自。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">任天堂 Switch 表現亮眼，調研預計 2019 年全球銷售量將超過 PS4</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://ccc.technews.tw/2018/11/30/strategy-analytics-says-nintendo-will-take-back-console-market-leadership/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fccc.technews.tw%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2Fstrategy-analytics-says-nintendo-will-take-back-console-market-leadership%2F&d=whdR2Uabg5GS9qNvSfZupv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=acb85ca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://ccc.technews.tw/2018/11/30/strategy-analytics-says-nintendo-will-take-back-console-market-leadership/</a><br />\n<br />\n數據來源：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Strategy Analytics: Nintendo to take back console market leadership in 2019</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2018-11-29-strategy-analytics-nintendo-to-take-back-console-market-leadership-in-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamesindustry.biz%2Farticles%2F2018-11-29-strategy-analytics-nintendo-to-take-back-console-market-leadership-in-2019&d=whdR2Uabg5GS9qNvSfZupv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=5fd67e6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2018-11-29-strategy-analytics-nintendo-to-take-back-console-market-leadership-in-2019</a>"},{"pid":"88045d74397e5766fdd2c8990166148da712bc6c","tid":945247,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"有無睇達哥爆機"},{"pid":"f6b9aef46cb31de7ee812859f17b217259df167d","tid":945247,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"值得一提的是，儘管許多人都不看好遊戲主機市場發展，但從報告來看 2018 年主機市場的表現仍舊強勁。報告指出，2018 年全球遊戲主機銷售量達 4,610 萬台，是 2010 年以來最高紀錄，主機所有權也就過去有上升，將近 45% 北美家庭和 20% 西歐家庭都擁有至少一台主機。<br />\n<br />\nStrategy Analytics 主管 David Watkins 表示，多年以來，許多權威人士都認為隨著行動裝置佔據主導地位、VR / AR 的出現，電視遊戲主機將會完結，然而和這些預期相反，全球電視遊戲主機市場仍然健康。<br />\n<br />\n「事實上有一種觀點認為，電視遊戲主機能夠維持如此長久的吸引力，正展現了那些替代遊戲平台的弱點和局限。」"},{"pid":"f84fe7240c528f4d1ae1c9696bf9346a52f4d5aa","tid":945247,"uid":126642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"屌，又出新switch 逼人換機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715a31cab39a2c0eb5cffd96c31093308de55989","tid":945247,"uid":46389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"原來XboxOne有1000萬部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c657a1aa9d9475bba4ba64fca37772add26fcd56","tid":945247,"uid":200828,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"Ps4出左咁耐都仲多過switch就出奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b88ac61f2964eb5bcfa01ef725097e534c9e1b","tid":945247,"uid":35918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"屌 仲以為總銷量超過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}